publicationXrefbbf.standardName: Molecular Pathways Controlling Autophagy in Pancreatic Cancer

publicationXrefcbd.standardName: Regulation and function of autophagy in pancreatic cancer

comments.content: This pathway demonstrates autophagy upregulation during pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma (PDAC). It covers autophagy accumulation as well as how this promotes cell proliferation in tumor microenvironment. Autophagy in PDAC affects mTOR signaling pathways as well as MAPK signaling pathway.
